   [;m│[0m  [48;2;17;24;39m[48;2;17;24;39mEach session can have a color for easy identification.[m                                                        [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m  [48;2;17;24;39m[48;2;17;24;39mColors appear as a gradient title bar in the sidebar and as a[m                                                 [;m│[0m   
